Wax Blockchain has come and exploded in popularity in recent years, it is a decentralized platform that uses blockchain technology to enable users to buy, sell, and trade virtual assets. It was launched in 2017 by William Quigley and Jonathan Yantis, and its primary focus was to create a market for trading virtual items from video games.

However, over time, Wax Blockchain has grown to become a popular platform for creating and trading NFTs. One of the unique aspects of Wax Blockchain is its use of the Proof of Stake consensus algorithm, which ensures faster transaction times and lower fees.

Additionally, Wax Blockchain's integration with the Ethereum blockchain allows for cross-chain interoperability, expanding its potential use cases. Today, Wax Blockchain is known for hosting a variety of popular games which we are going to check the top five today. That been said, letâ€™s dive in:

1. ## **Taco**

Genre: Card Game  
Tokenomics: $TACO (Main Currency), $SHING (Currency of Taco Universe), $ONI (Strategic Token)

Play Option: Free-to-play & Play-to-earn

Overview:  
![][image1]  
[Source](https://pbs.twimg.com/media/FteQcxMWcAAM7Kt?format=jpg&name=small)

[Taco](https://p2eanalytics.com/blockchain-games/taco/profile) is a collectible card game that allows players to build a team of unique taco characters and battle against other players for rewards.

The gameplay in Taco involves collecting and trading taco cards, each with a different set of stats, abilities, and rarity levels. You can use these cards to build a deck of up to six tacos, which you can then use to battle against other players in real-time matches.

During each match, players take turns choosing which taco in their deck to play, strategically placing them on a game board that consists of six rows and three columns. Each taco has its own movement range and attack range, and you must strategically move your tacos around the board while attacking your opponent's tacos.

As you progress through the game, you can earn rewards such as new taco cards and in-game currency, which you can use to upgrade your existing tacos and buy new cards from the marketplace.

Altogether, Taco offers a unique blend of strategy and collectibility, making it an exciting and engaging game for both casual and hardcore gamers alike.

2. ## **Alien Worlds**

Genre: Metaverse  
Tokenomics: $TLM  
Play Option: Free-to-play & Play-to-earn

Overview:  
![][image2]  
[Source](https://pbs.twimg.com/media/FuhRDVyWIAAt9OE?format=jpg&name=small)

[Alien World](https://p2eanalytics.com/blockchain-games/alien-worlds/profile) is a gaming platform that allows players to mine a cryptocurrency called Trilium while exploring virtual worlds filled with unique alien creatures and resources.

You begin by choosing a planet to explore and a land parcel to mine on. Each parcel of land contains a set number of resources and can be mined once per day, with the amount of Trilium earned depending on the rarity and abundance of the resources found.

As you mine your land parcels, you can also encounter alien creatures, which can be captured and used to battle against other players in an arena-style game. These creatures also have their own rarity levels and stats, and can be traded on the marketplace for Trilium or other in-game items.

One of the most unique aspects of Alien World is its use of the Wax blockchain to ensure the ownership and authenticity of all in-game assets. This means that all land parcels and alien creatures are tokenized and can be bought, sold, or traded on external marketplaces.

In general, Alien World offers a unique combination of gaming pattern, and exploration, making it a fascinating and engaging platform for players of all levels of experience.

3. ## **Prospectors**

Genre: Massive Multiplayer Online Role-Playing Game  
Tokenomics: $PGL  
Play Option: Play-to-earn

Overview:  
![][image3]  
[source](https://pbs.twimg.com/media/FrVdV60XoAADohF?format=jpg&name=small)

[Prospectors](https://p2eanalytics.com/blockchain-games/prospectors/profile) is a strategy game that simulates a 19th-century gold rush, allowing you to mine for resources, build your own economies, and compete against other players for wealth and power.

The game is set in a virtual world that closely resembles the American West during the gold rush era, complete with its own currency, economy, and resources. You begin by selecting a character and establishing a settlement, which serves as the foundation for your future activities in the game.

One of the primary activities in Prospectors is mining, which involves using various tools and equipment to extract valuable resources from the game world. These resources can then be sold on the marketplace for profit, or used to build new structures and facilities that can help you expand your operations.

You can also engage in trade with other players, forming alliances and partnerships to create larger economies and dominate the game world. The game's economy is entirely player-driven, meaning that the value of resources and goods is determined by supply and demand, creating a dynamic and ever-changing marketplace.

Overall, Prospectors offers a unique blend of strategy, and simulation, making it an engaging and challenging game for you interested in the virtual economy and the gold rush era of American history.

4. ## **NFT Panda: World Of fantasy**

Genre: Role-Playing Game (RPG)  
Tokenomics: $BAM  
Play Option: Play-to-earn

Overview:  
![][image4]  
[source](https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/1360196210011865089/1624012910/600x200)

[NFT Panda](https://p2eanalytics.com/blockchain-games/nft-pandaworld-of-fantasy/profile) is a collectible game that allows you to collect and trade unique digital pandas in the form of NFTs. Each panda has its own distinct traits and rarity levels, making them valuable and sought-after among collectors.

You can acquire NFT Pandas by purchasing them on the marketplace or by participating in various in-game activities and events. Once acquired, you can trade, sell, or hold onto your pandas, much like traditional collectibles.

In addition to collecting and trading pandas, you can also breed your pandas to create new and unique offspring. Breeding involves using two pandas with compatible traits, and can result in the creation of a rare or even legendary panda with unique attributes.

Altogether, NFT Panda offers a fun and engaging collectible game experience for players interested in NFTs. Its integration with the Wax blockchain allows for seamless transactions and low fees, making it accessible to a wider audience of players and collectors.

5. ## **Farmers World**

Genre: Farming Game  
Tokenomics: There are 3 main resources in Farmers World: Wood, Food and Gold corresponding to 3 tokens: $FWW (Wood), $FWF (Food), $FWG (Gold).  
Play Option: Play-to-earn

Overview:  
![][image5]  
[Source](https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/1405806792530022400/1625209732/600x200)

[Farmers World](https://p2eanalytics.com/blockchain-games/farmers-world/profile) is a game that allows you to become virtual farmers, building and managing your own farms and growing crops to sell and trade with other players.

You begin by creating your own avatar and selecting a plot of land on which to build your farm. You then plant crops, raise animals, and invest in various farm upgrades and technologies to improve their yield and profitability.

You can also form alliances and partnerships with other farmers, creating larger economies and cooperatives that can compete against other players or dominate the game world.

One of the unique features of Farmers World is its use of real-world weather data to influence the game's virtual weather and crop yield. This creates a more realistic and immersive farming experience, and requires players to adapt and adjust their strategies based on the current weather conditions.

Overall, Farmers World offers a unique and engaging farming simulation experience, allowing you to explore the world of agriculture and trade in a virtual setting. Its use of real-world data adds a level of authenticity and transparency to the game, making it a fascinating and rewarding experience for players of all levels of experience.
